  "label": "Rovik Sarn",
  "description": "This individual is an undead human of late middle years, marked by pallid light skin stretched tight over prominent cheekbones and a jaw set by long deprivation. Gray eyes sit deep in bruised sockets, and gray hair falls in an unkempt, thinning mane that exposes a high, scar-lined scalp. The mouth is drawn back in a permanent rictus that reveals cracked teeth and desiccated gums, while the hands retain a grave-stiff curl from rigor long since made habitual. The overall physique is lean and corded, with sunken musculature and knotted joints that signal an existence sustained beyond death rather than by it.",
